### ============================================================
### 1. ROOT
### ============================================================

### Cek server berjalan
GET {{baseUrl}}/


### ============================================================
### 2. AUTH
### ============================================================

### [AUTH] Register - Daftar akun baru
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Budi Santoso",
  "username": "budi123",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### [AUTH] Login - Masuk dan dapatkan token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "budi_updated",
  "password": "passwordBaru789"
}

###

### [AUTH] Refresh Token - Perbarui auth token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "authToken": "{{authToken}}",
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### [AUTH] Logout - Keluar dan hapus token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "authToken": "{{authToken}}"
}

###


### ============================================================
### 3. USERS (Profil) - Memerlukan Bearer Token
### ============================================================

### [USER] Get Me - Ambil data profil saya
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### [USER] Put Me - Ubah nama dan username
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Budi Santoso Updated",
  "username": "budi_updated"
}

###

### [USER] Put My Password - Ubah kata sandi
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "passwordBaru789",
  "newPassword": "passwordBaru999"
}

###

### [USER] Put My About - Ubah deskripsi/tentang saya
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me/about
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "about": "Saya adalah pustakawan di perpustakaan kota."
}

###

### [USER] Put My Photo - Upload foto profil
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me/photo
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="foto.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< C:\Users\hp\Documents\Semester 6\PAM\Praktikum\uts-proyek\pam-2026-ifs23015-proyek1-be\foto.jpg
--boundary--

###


### ============================================================
### 4. IMAGES (Public - Tanpa Token)
### ============================================================

### [IMAGE] Ambil foto profil user berdasarkan ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/images/users/{{userId}}

###

### [IMAGE] Ambil cover buku berdasarkan ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/images/books/{{bookId}}

###


### ============================================================
### 5. BOOKS - Memerlukan Bearer Token
### ============================================================

### [BOOK] Get All Books - Ambil semua buku
GET {{baseUrl}}/books
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### [BOOK] Get All Books - Dengan filter pencarian
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?search=Harry Potter&page=1&perPage=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### [BOOK] Get All Books - Dengan filter genre
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?genre=Fantasi&page=1&perPage=5
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### [BOOK] Get Book by ID - Ambil detail buku
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/{{bookId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### [BOOK] Post Book - Tambah buku baru
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Harry Potter dan Batu Bertuah",
  "author": "J.K. Rowling",
  "genre": "Fantasi",
  "stock": 5
}

###

### [BOOK] Put Book - Update data buku
PUT {{baseUrl}}/books/{{bookId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Harry Potter dan Batu Bertuah (Edisi Revisi)",
  "author": "J.K. Rowling",
  "genre": "Fantasi",
  "stock": 10
}

###

### [BOOK] Put Cover Book - Upload cover buku
PUT {{baseUrl}}/books/{{bookId}}/cover
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cover"; filename="foto.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< C:\Users\hp\Documents\Semester 6\PAM\Praktikum\uts-proyek\pam-2026-ifs23015-proyek1-be\foto.jpg
--boundary--

###

### [BOOK] Delete Book - Hapus buku
### Catatan: buku tidak bisa dihapus jika masih ada peminjaman aktif
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/books/{{bookId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###


### ============================================================
### 6. BORROWINGS (Peminjaman) - Memerlukan Bearer Token
### ============================================================

### [BORROWING] Get All Borrowings - Ambil semua peminjaman
GET {{baseUrl}}/borrowings
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### [BORROWING] Get All Borrowings - Filter status "borrowed"
GET {{baseUrl}}/borrowings?status=borrowed&page=1&perPage=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### [BORROWING] Get All Borrowings - Filter status "returned"
GET {{baseUrl}}/borrowings?status=returned&page=1&perPage=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### [BORROWING] Get All Borrowings - Dengan pencarian nama peminjam
GET {{baseUrl}}/borrowings?search=Andi&page=1&perPage=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### [BORROWING] Get Borrowing Summary - Ringkasan data peminjaman
GET {{baseUrl}}/borrowings/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### [BORROWING] Get Borrowing by ID - Ambil detail peminjaman
GET {{baseUrl}}/borrowings/{{borrowingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### [BORROWING] Post Borrowing - Catat peminjaman baru
POST {{baseUrl}}/borrowings
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "{{bookId}}",
  "borrowerName": "Andi Prasetyo"
}

###

### [BORROWING] Put Borrowing - Update status peminjaman
PUT {{baseUrl}}/borrowings/{{borrowingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "borrowerName": "Andi Prasetyo",
  "status": "returned"
}

###

### [BORROWING] Delete Borrowing - Hapus data peminjaman
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/borrowings/{{borrowingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###